      "content": "but that's the thing, i don't want to take care of this version of me. i don't want to keep \"trying\" to find ways to make it easier, because it never actually gets easier. it's just constant friction. sometimes i wonder if maybe the only way to actually stop the noise and the exhaustion is just to... not be here anymore. is it even wrong to think that peace might only be possible if everything just stopped?",
